cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper is primarily focused on the application of deep learning techniques, specifically in the area of distributed computation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the challenges of distributed computation on WAN connected devices, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel algorithm for compressing worker updates, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
